         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1865 ¶  20th March ¶ Dr Mueller F.R.S. ¶  ¶ &amp;c ¶  ¶ &amp;c ¶  ¶ &amp;c ¶ Melbourne ¶  ¶ In reference to the request contained in your letter of the 26th June last, ¶  addressed to H E. Governor Hampton, to be...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">65.03.20</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Frederick Barlee</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Colonial Secretary's Office</seg>, acc. 49, vol. 39, no. 190, State Records Office of Western Australia, Perth. </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>1865<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS is in a letterbook with the year entered at the top of the page.</p>
               </note> 20th March</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Mueller F.R.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reference to the request contained in your letter of the 26th June last,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to J. Hampton, 26 June 1864.</p>
               </note> addressed to H E. Governor Hampton, to be furnished with such specimens of the Poison plants of this Colony as would enable you to experiment on them. I have much pleasure, by direction of His Excellency, in forwarding to your address three specimens of these plants,<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Marginal note: '<seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Separate</hi>
                     </seg>.'</p>
               </note> which have been collected expressly for the object you have in view, and which are known here as the Rock Poison Plant, York road Poison Plant, and the Box Poison Plant.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Governor Hampton trusts that these specimens will be sufficient for your purpose and directs me to add that he will feel obliged by any information in regard to them, which you may be able at any future time to afford.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">x-ref.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">F. P. B.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
